timing_create_...use_ideal_slew(25.10)  timing_create_...use_ideal_slew(25.10)

Name
       timing_create_clock_use_ideal_slew

Syntax
       timing_create_clock_use_ideal_slew

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       Enables the use of ideal slew at the inputs of the clock driver cells.

       When  set  to  true, the software detects created clocks, and uses zero
       input slew. Other slew values,  including  those  set  using  set_anno-
       tated_transition command, will be ignored.

       When set to false, the software honors set_annotated_transition command
       settings.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

